{"tid":1486731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「連登仔」落實13國再登報 追究警方上周日濫暴","createTime":"2019-08-19T03:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T03:57:31.000Z","uid":258489,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"725c0a55671d6e3921267e47b358d3c711d9e572","tid":1486731,"uid":258489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"上周日警方在多區武力清場，網上討論區「連登」部分會員再發眾籌全球登報，共籌得180萬美元。眾籌團隊昨公布，落實於13個國家或地區、共18份報章上刊登廣告，並將於8月19至30日陸續見報。<br />\n <br />\n早前有連登會員組成「G20團隊」，在G20峰會舉行期間，在全球多份報章登報反對修例，而8月11日多區再爆警民衝突，有少女疑被布袋彈打盲眼，警方再被受質疑過分使用武力。G20團隊昨透過社交平台專頁表示，聯同連登其他會員組成的「我要攬炒」團隊，落實於多國報章上登廣告，把上周日警方的做法公諸國際，8月底行動包括「爭取各國同時制裁港共一干人等之戰爭罪行」。<br />\n<br />\n該眾籌活動上周日發起，目標籌100萬美元，但僅兩小時就達標，最終籌得180萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/126994627339633/posts/2464096976962708?s=100000597414935&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F126994627339633%2Fposts%2F2464096976962708%3Fs%3D100000597414935%26sfns%3Dmo&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=543f1662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/126994627339633/posts/2464096976962708?s=100000597414935&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"d7f3a7c38f8d3b94aa2de71a3f29291c2c567eac","tid":1486731,"uid":258489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZiqBBJd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiqBBJd.jpg&h=9d7de898&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3334335efb638d0c251a62da71d440ad4a29e525","tid":1486731,"uid":258489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccca85cb11d85a8ccbccae7ac4d689e65584e97c","tid":1486731,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face